title: Zelliack - Noir Tone EP (2012) Digital Rip 320 kbps {Protest}
description:
Zelliack is a Soul/R&B fusion group that consists of former TesseracT frontman Elliot Coleman and Zack Ordway. The tunes are very sexy so don't be surprised to find out that you aren't wearing pants any more after listening to this. 

Track listing:
1) Autumn in Analog
2) Hargrove
3) Without a Doubt
4) These Hands
5) Call Me Old Fashioned
